export const Device = {

  mobileM: `(min-width: ${size.mobileM})`,
  mobileL: `(min-width: ${size.mobileL})`,
  laptop: `(min-width: ${size.laptop})`,
  laptopL: `(min-width: ${size.laptopL})`,
